    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my kid's school just sent out a notice that they're adding some new stuff to the curriculum about gender identity and stuff. i'm a bit confused about why they're doing this now and what all the different perspectives are around this. can u help me understand the different sides of the debate?",
