    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for explaining. i noticed you mentioned it's a \"well-intentioned effort\" to make kids feel safe. is that generally considered the main reason why schools are doing it, or is it more of a political thing? like, is there a consensus among experts that this actually helps kids, or is that just one way of looking at it?",
